data.description: Fully Renovated 4+3+Office/den+Bonus+Shop, On 2.05 Acres with 1.3 Acres of fenced pasture to the South. CAMAS SCHOOLS, EVERYTHING IS NEW~~New Doors, New Flooring, New Appliances, New Kitchen with Soft Close, Quartz, Pantry, New HVAC system (heatpump and furnace), New Pex plumbing, New water softner with house filter, New decks, New Roof, New Siding, New Paint, New Gutters, New Windows, New Water Heater. Hi-speed internet, both sellers work from home. Storage galore~Bring all of your toys~Attached 24x24 garage 576sf with new garage door opener and attic storage. Garage addition 24x14 336sf. 1982 barn conversion 2020 to shop has new concrete floors, garage door opener and garage doors 1150sf (220 volt electricity, water) RV hookup. Possible assumable VA 3.25% for qualifying Veterans. Please click virtual tour for more pictures.
